    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"meaningful impact\" thing feels like a lie people just tell to keep everyone moving in the machine. it feels like we're all just parts in a system that doesn't care if we break or not. if the system is just about productivity and roles, and i can't play those roles... then what's actually the point of participating?",
